Package: plocate-gui
Version: 0.2.0
Architecture: all
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Maintainer: plocate-gui developers
Depends: python3 (>= 3.8),
         python3-pyqt6,
         plocate,
         policykit-1,
         libxcb-cursor0
Description: Fast GUI file search using plocate
 A PyQt6-based graphical interface for the plocate command-line utility.
 Features include:
  - Interactive search with debounced auto-completion
  - Multi-keyword AND search matching plocate CLI semantics
  - Category filtering by file type (Documents, Images, Video, etc.)
  - Dual database support (system and external media)
  - File metadata columns: Size, Modified time, Creation time
  - Non-blocking database updates via pkexec
  - Keyboard shortcuts for common operations
  - Configurable result limits
Homepage: https://github.com/dmnmsc/plocate-gui
